Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.16,0:02:01.06,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我從未夢想過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.80,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}會前往凍成堅冰的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:06.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}去尋找你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.16,0:02:11.32,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}願望　飛舞到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.61,0:02:16.53,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}寂寞的夜空中　破碎了
