Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.17,0:00:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.03,0:00:18.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能進行左手再生治療…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹部的幹細胞發現異常
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說可能是因為Gundam的光束兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:28.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引起細胞障礙導致的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.88,0:00:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的哦  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.80,0:00:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要乖乖回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.59,0:01:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就去找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:55.39,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}美國  聯合國會場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:55.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於Celestial Being的多次兇惡的恐怖襲擊行為
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:03:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯合  人類革新聯盟和AEU締結了軍事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.24,0:03:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在此宣佈  要在聯合國的管理下\N為了消滅Celestial Being而採取軍事行動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:18.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三方陣營在聯合國的管理下發表了軍事同盟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.44,0:03:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由此  將誕生有史以來最大規模的聯合國軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來事情正像Celestial Being預想的那樣發展呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近過激的武力介入  是為了使聯合國軍隊統一的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該可以這麼考慮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使世界團結一致
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Celestial Being的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用戰爭來否定戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了獲得和平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這就是你所希望的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃的第一階段總算是結束了  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體的行動成了導火線  這是否能改變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.79,0:04:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各國的軍事基地因三位一體而受到了重創
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種狀況下即使統一軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該也不會有什麼結果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只會招致世人的失望和反感
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼內幕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說實話  我感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.61,0:04:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吠陀的訊息未明示的三位一體的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於吠陀的資料被竄改這一事實的無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:30.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.75,0:04:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來自皇·李·諾瑞加的密碼訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請Meister和機體一起返回普特利麥奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.79,0:04:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK  有作戰會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回宇宙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.25,0:04:53.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先看看聯合國軍隊的動向
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.07,0:04:58.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你預測過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此  不預先準備一下的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊恩  你能否帶上拉塞去拿GN ARMS呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN ARMS生產好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:12.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之只有一台
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.46,0:05:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,餘下的成員準備進行飛上來的Gundam的回收作業
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:27.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於要投入GN ARMS了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況所迫  不得已而為之啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:37.93,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}聯合  美國  伊利諾斯基地
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐  是關於從新型Gundam奪來的光刀的調查結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.58,0:05:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.93,0:05:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來Celestial Being內部出現了叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.55,0:05:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說叛徒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.17,0:05:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.56,0:05:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還送來了與Gundam同型號的發動機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.41,0:06:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及搭設了這種發動機的MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還是30台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才作了那樣的發表
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.29,0:06:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提供來的機體的機師\N應該會從Over Flags的隊員中進行挑選吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.07,0:06:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然  隊長會是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我堅決反對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.26,0:06:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用Flag來打倒Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:27.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在霍華德·梅森的墓前這麼發過誓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過隊長  以Flag的性能是抵擋不了Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.50,0:06:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢大丈夫  一言既出駟馬難追
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:43.83,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}人革聯  俄羅斯南部  駐軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.45,0:06:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam的主要機構…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:07:01.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據資料  正式名稱好像叫做GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分配給我們人革聯的GN Drive有10個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.82,0:07:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校  機師的人選由你來定
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我來做新型機的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.56,0:07:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.49,0:07:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說少尉釋放的腦量子波會對長翅膀的機師產生影響
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個優點  不使用就可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不這樣可就不好辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:31.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}AEU  法國  基地內士官宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機師候補的話  集中AEU所屬國的王牌就行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  是否要加入那個男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:50.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大校  是我  帕特里克·克拉薩烏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.41,0:07:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事  少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.24,0:07:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想請大校吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.19,0:07:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:03.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界現在正要迎來巨大的變革期
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此你有考慮過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…真是無可救藥的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.71,0:08:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我準備一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:25.84,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}線性火車公司  會長別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是JNN嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們說  對此無可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.76,0:08:29.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.48,0:08:33.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人氣真是不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不談這個  機體的運輸好像很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借款之事就讓我去辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那·哈貝總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:46.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就開門見山直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:53.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否把運輸中的新型機中的1台讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不管是聯合還是AEU都行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:04.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您以總裁的權限讓我加入軍隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你隸屬外籍戰士部隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.49,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是加里·比亞吉少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.15,0:09:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說你很有天賦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.52,0:09:16.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  你為何那麼想要駕駛那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.35,0:09:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠了某個人3次人情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這有點關係
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我的感覺  我認為在以後的未來  傭兵將變得不再需要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少想去一個能夠作戰的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.62,0:09:32.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了  這只是我的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.75,0:09:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能考慮一下  總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.01,0:09:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪那Celestial什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取材空手而歸  該怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才說總裁在面談…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.28,0:10:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.62,0:10:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是JNN的特派員
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想問兩三個問題  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.57,0:10:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JNN的記者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可以  但我正有急事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否在車上談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:29.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用問了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是叫絹江·克洛斯羅德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.69,0:10:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  有你這樣的美女記者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.31,0:10:47.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  要問我的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.11,0:10:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果搞錯了請見諒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比亞吉先生你之前是否會見了火車公司的總裁拉古那·哈貝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  見了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.85,0:10:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,談了些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.56,0:11:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從事的是流通行業
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了確認物資的流通而會見了總裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個特意去見總裁？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:10.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是私事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  私事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能告訴我些關於這些物資的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN…Drive？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是與線性火車公司有關的什麼器材嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.61,0:11:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是驅動MS的引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧  是Celestial Being擁有的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那個克魯吉斯的少年兵為機師的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:47.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯的…少年兵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.96,0:11:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:56.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誘拐  洗腦  接受戰鬥訓練  並成為遊擊兵這一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.24,0:11:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我所為
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:02.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個戰爭狂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰爭喜歡到了忍受不了的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.17,0:12:12.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為人類的本能衝動而生的最惡劣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…又出去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.68,0:12:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那隻鬼鬼祟祟的老鼠處理了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:37.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一舉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這是個威脅輿論支持的好活動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.91,0:12:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  貪心的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸  爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.24,0:13:22.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙  沙慈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.85,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(500,500)}聯合  高軌道平台
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.31,0:13:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得亞歷桑德羅大人您沒必要特地和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你辛苦得來的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.76,0:13:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我親眼看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  這是柯納一族長久以來的夙願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞歷桑德羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:10.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  應該說柯納一家在好幾代之前就策劃了對計劃的介入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但只要吠陀還在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就什麼都做不了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.03,0:14:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這個時候  很偶然的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的面前有天使降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.44,0:14:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你  李本茲·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.41,0:14:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我報答您把我撿回來的大恩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到你要查明本體的所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.07,0:14:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花了那麼長的時間  非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李本茲  你真是我的天使啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:45.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}非洲大陸  西北部
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前一直讓我到處工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.55,0:14:49.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在突然中止聯絡  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.35,0:14:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別問我啊  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅長考慮這些複雜的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克哥就是這種類型呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿我當笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:00.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.61,0:15:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你個哈羅  欠砍是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  哈羅是三位一體不可或缺的戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.80,0:15:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  大哥  開玩笑的  玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.00,0:15:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉古那發來了任務計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:14.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內容跟以前的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:17.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰在三天後開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:18.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就等著這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.80,0:15:23.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.97,0:15:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼通過防衛系統的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:30.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  既然你們發現了這裡  那就別想輕易離開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.33,0:15:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  邁克爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:35.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位美女  我記得在吠陀的資料裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.96,0:15:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能被記住是我的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Celestial Being的特工
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是我的搭檔紅龍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:48.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯的男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能來到這裡就知道你們的能力很高
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  找我們有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是來打聲招呼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體小隊跟我們一樣隸屬Celestial Being
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.46,0:16:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為特工的我們支援你們是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:13.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是被你們的Gundam攻擊了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件事我也有所耳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.94,0:16:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我不是他們那邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:24.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是中立派嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我遵從的是伊奧利亞·修亨伯格提出的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.83,0:16:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:41.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  王留美
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.64,0:16:45.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等需要的時候就看你的援助了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.63,0:16:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:52.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答應不告訴他們  告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼放他們回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.91,0:17:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  能用的牌自然是多多益善了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.36,0:17:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是美女  真是美女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.64,0:17:10.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別帶有偏見  別帶有偏見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celestial Being和他們敵對…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:20.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為三位一體引發了世界的變革
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.53,0:17:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就那麼厭惡現在的世界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我覺得不改變的話  破壞了也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.46,0:17:38.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  著艦完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:45.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情況如何
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到目前為止還沒有變化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.02,0:17:49.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體也沒有活動
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.11,0:17:51.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,違反命令的懲罰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候有這規定的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.42,0:17:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.36,0:18:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐  三位一體開始行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.30,0:18:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:12.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特  他們的攻擊目標是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:17.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進線路上的軍事基地是人革聯廣州軍區
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:21.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(0,500)}人革聯  廣州方面軍駐地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測班呼叫所有人員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判定為新型Gundam的三台MS正從S9788方向飛來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將對本基地進行軍事介入…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:30.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們為之前的事等了很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要好好幹一場  行嗎  大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作戰上沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一架來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我中  給我中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕  集中火力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打我後面  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.45,0:18:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雜魚  開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該死  見鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該收場了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始對接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.03,0:19:11.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.22,0:19:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Exia嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.60,0:19:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.75,0:19:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是10機的編隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.12,0:19:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.42,0:19:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  放出GN粒子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是Celestial Being嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:31.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頂武GN-X部隊  開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是虎之子的10台機體
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別被打成重傷哦  上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:41.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這種機動性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.13,0:19:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這性能真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  這機體  厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam已經不足為懼了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:19:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的對手是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:17.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機體可以跟上我的反應速度
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Gundam的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟敢把Fang…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.49,0:20:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許爭論
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天這樣就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  中校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.59,0:20:36.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看下面的基地
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明受到了那麼嚴重的破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉你是第一次嘗到這種味道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.50,0:20:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.70,0:20:56.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.34,0:20:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體似乎從戰鬥空域離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.57,0:21:09.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人革聯方面把搭載了太陽爐的MS投入了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.27,0:21:11.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  有情報從吠陀那裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.28,0:21:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就會變成Gundam之間的戰鬥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣  世界仍在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.03,0:21:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前面到底會有什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.40,0:21:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊請  亞歷桑德羅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:07.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是吠陀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.99,0:22:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·修亨伯格
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  作為Celestial Being基礎的系統
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.29,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}同じ笑顔してた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:25.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}そんな僕らも幾年も重ねすぎて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:28.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}すれ違う景色を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:34.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}受け入れられずにもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:41.24,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無駄なプライド捨て去り
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:46.93,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この世界に優しさを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.12,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}I Gotta Say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:53.50,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}勇気を見せつけても　強がっても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:58.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一人では生きられない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}あの日の約束なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}心の深くに残っているよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.98,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:18.42,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:30.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.92,0:22:18.29,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有著相同的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:25.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那樣的我們也已過了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.53,0:22:28.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交錯的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.06,0:22:34.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無法接受並急躁著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.24,0:22:41.24,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}捨棄了無用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.56,0:22:46.93,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}給予這世界以溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:48.12,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:53.50,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便顯示出勇氣　即便逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.65,0:22:58.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一個人亦是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.76,0:23:02.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心靈深處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.87,0:23:12.98,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延續...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:18.42,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由於不可忘記　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:23.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要離去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:30.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}還要留在這廣闊大地同伴們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.99,0:23:37.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型的MS對Gundam發起了攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.46,0:23:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對追求著根除戰爭夢想的人們的判罪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.87,0:23:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  「毀滅之路」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是世界的回應


